rComments: insistence of her own method and poor management of time
More of a class in English grammar than art. Not in touch with contemporary culture and practice. Insists on using her specific methods.
I highly recommend this course and professor Heard.
Excellent introductory course to painting - Prof. Heard provided a great deal of information and taught a lot of different techniques. Me wants moar :)

Entertaining lectures. Good visual aids helped complex subject matter. Overall, a lot of material to learn, but that's what you get with these intro courses. Professor Heard helped to make it interesting.

replacement for L.
